  06 Jun 2005; Sergey Kuleshov <svyatogor@gentoo.org> gajim-0.7.1.ebuild:
  Added nls and spell USE flags.

*gajim-0.7.1 (05 Jun 2005)

  05 Jun 2005; Sergey Kuleshov <svyatogor@gentoo.org> +gajim-0.7.1.ebuild:
